active.description: Whether the creative is active. Applicable to all creative types.

DISPLAY and DISPLAY_INTERSTITIAL refer to rendering either on desktop or on mobile devices or in mobile apps for regular or interstitial ads, respectively. thirdPartyUrls.description: Third-party URLs for tracking in-stream creative events. Applicable to the following creative types: all INSTREAM_VIDEO, all INSTREAM_AUDIO, and all VPAID.
